item.title: CVE-2023-44306|2024-10-01T14:45:00.749Z -- dell -- dell%20powerprotect%20data%20manager%20dm5500%20appliance
item.description: Dell DM5500 contains a path traversal vulnerability in the appliance. A remote attacker with high privileges could potentially exploit this vulnerability to overwrite configuration files stored on the server filesystem.
